original: Kärnborg, Jonas Bertil, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 1/3/04 i Gbg. G. 32 m. tandl. Aina Berg. Barn: Ingela f. 36, Agneta 38, Maria 44, Jonas 46. — Studrex. v. Gbgs h. latin 22, Cand. med. dent. i Berlin 24, tandl :kand. 26, tandl. 29. Prakt, i Gbg sed. 29, skoltandl. v. Gbgs folksk. sed. 32, olika förordn. v. Gbgs komm. tandpolikiin.
translated: Kärnborg, Jonas Bertil, dentist, Gothenburg, born on 1/3/04 in Gothenburg. Married in 1932 to dentist Aina Berg. Children: Ingela born in 1936, Agneta born in 1938, Maria born in 1944, Jonas born in 1946. - Attended Gothenburg higher Latin school until 1922, received a dental degree (Cand. med. dent.) in Berlin in 1924, completed dental studies in 1926, became a licensed dentist in 1929. Practiced in Gothenburg since 1929, worked as a school dentist at Gothenburg elementary schools since 1932, held various appointments at the Gothenburg municipal dental polyclinic.
